I slipped and fell.

17
00:06:03,415 --> 00:06:04,812
- Fighting is never justified.

18
00:06:04,832 --> 00:06:06,229
- I know.

19
00:06:07,450 --> 00:06:09,493
Go have your snack.

20
00:06:10,203 --> 00:06:11,245
Thank you.

21
