Let's pick bamboo grass.

24
00:06:22,424 --> 00:06:23,882
Big brother!

25
00:06:26,970 --> 00:06:29,430
I want to pick bamboo grass.

26
00:06:34,311 --> 00:06:36,604
You promised to go with me.

27
00:06:36,771 --> 00:06:37,980
I've got homework.

28
00:06:44,487 --> 00:06:46,196
That's not homework.

29
00:06:46,364 --> 00:06:47,740
It's an English magazine.

30
00:06:51,119 --> 00:06:52,745
What a stupid moustache.

31
00:06:53,204 --> 00:06:55,789
He's a famous Italian aircraft designer.

32
00:06:56,092 --> 00:06:58,345
His name is Caproni.

33
00:06:58,365 --> 00:07:00,618
It says he's a count.

34
