- Your face is scratched.

35
00:07:02,368 --> 00:07:03,911
- Leave it alone.

36
00:07:04,341 --> 00:07:06,759
I better put some iodine on it.

37
00:07:06,885 --> 00:07:08,802
Would you be quiet?

38
00:07:19,606 --> 00:07:21,982
Big brother, what are you doing?

39
00:07:22,192 --> 00:07:23,817
You're not allowed up here.

40
00:07:23,985 --> 00:07:25,486
You're not wearing glasses.

41
00:07:25,612 --> 00:07:29,990
Focusing on the stars should improve my eyesight.

42
00:07:31,670 --> 00:07:33,151
- Mother will scold you.

43
00:07:33,171 --> 00:07:34,652
- A shooting star!

44
00:07:36,039 --> 00:07:37,748
There's another one.

45
00:07:39,010 --> 00:07:40,102
They're pretty.

46
00:07:40,122 --> 00:07:41,214
See?

47
00:07:41,234 --> 00:07:42,326
Like that.

48
00:07:43,672 --> 00:07:45,839
There's so many of them.

49
00:08:23,211 --> 00:08:25,045
I'm a Japanese boy.

50
